parameters: Do you want to continue pursuing Court Magician Eratoma?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then decide)

Clea: I've always felt that something was off. There must be
something we don't know...

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: Hey hey, meeting in a place like
this!

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: Did you come to see me, by any
chance?
Maid Amina: I think it's a big misunderstanding, Master.
Clea: Why are we in a place like this...

Priestess Sophia: Excuse us, may we pass? We have some
business with the man who fled to the back.

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: Amina, tell me! When was the
last time I was glared at with such a scary face?

Maid Amina: Yes, Master. It's been since the incident at
Beach Lepton where I failed to seduce a female customer.

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: What a waste of a beautiful
woman. Beautiful people should always be smiling, don't you
think?

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: By the way... do you recognize
this emblem?
Priestess Sophia: The three-legged... hawk emblem...
Priestess Sophia: Why... Could it be...!

Lewd, the Profligate Noble: We are sinners who wield short
swords in the darkness for the same master as you.
Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: That's right, isn't it...
Priestess Sophia: Everyone, run away! This man is--

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: As expected, the power to defeat
a dragon. This can be considered a threat.

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: Well, the time for stalling is
over, and there hasn't been an order to kill you all.

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: Let's meet again, Alicia-
senpai.

Clea: Let's chase after them. I still can't believe it...
They pointed their swords at us.

Mage Relm: Of course! Those people could be the suspects of
the incident!
Thief Nora: She was so kind... why... *sniff* why...

Clea: Let's leave the conversation for later. Right now,
it's important to chase after them.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: Dealing with acquaintances...
sigh, this kind of job really brings me down.

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: You probably think that way,
Alicia-senpai, right?

Priestess Sophia: W-Who are you... and why... when I was in
Ishaker... why...

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: There were various things that
happened within the organization because you all left on
your own.

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: Well, you have a role of showing
the fate of those who acted on their own.

Imperial Dark Faction Lewd: Now, let's return to the dimly
lit place. It's just the time for you to experience what you
did in the past.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
